Homepage: http://kosagi.com/
Vcs-Git: git://github.com/xobs/novena-firstrun.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/xobs/novena-firstrun

Package: novena-firstrun
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Script to set up Novena when it is first booted
 When a Novena is booted for the first time, there are various config knobs
 that will need to be tuned on a per-user basis.  Things like timezone and
 keyboard layout.  novena-firstrun will take care of this.
